      </p>
      <p>
        <inline name="agenda item name">Sport for development and peace: building a peaceful and better world through sport and the Olympic ideal</inline>
      </p>
      <p>
        <docTitle>Resolution adopted by the General Assembly on 6 September 2024</docTitle>
      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docProponent refersTo="#noMainCommittee">[without reference to a Main Committee (<inline name="originating document">A/78/L.107</inline>)]</docProponent>
